<subSubSection pageId="131" pageNumber="528" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="131.[161,1369,2256,2879]" pageId="131" pageNumber="528">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[163,514,2729,2762]" pageId="131" pageNumber="528">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Least Concern on The IUCN Red List. Therese’s White-toothed Shrew has a wide distribution and does not face any major threats.
</paragraph>
